lead_paragraph: A disillusioned Jason Day arrived five years ago for his first Masters but he was hardly full of eager anticipation about the prospect of finally playing Augusta National competitively.

headline.print_headline: Masters Runner-Up Finish in 2011 Turned Day's Career Around
